          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>Military Tribunals for Terrorists Act of 2013 - Requires trial only by a military commission for any foreign national who: (1) engages or has engaged in an offense relating to a terrorist attack against persons or property in the United States or U.S. government property or personnel outside the United States, and (2) is subject to trial for that offense by a military commission under the Uniform Code of Military Justice.</p>]]></text>
          <actionDate>2013-03-12</actionDate>
          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        </item>
